---
import Blockquote from "@/components/elements/Blockquote.astro";
import PageHeading from "@/components/elements/PageHeading.astro";
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import { Brain, Code, GraduationCap, Users, Target } from "lucide-react";
---

<PageLayout title={"About me"} description={"Who is me?"}>
  <PageHeading
    heading={"Welcome to my profile!"}
    paragraph={"Hello! I'm Dorian Karter, a seasoned Full Stack Staff Software Engineer with a passion for writing clean, efficient, and scalable code."}
    tags={[
      "💜 Elixir",
      "💙 TypeScript",
      "⚛️ React",
      "🐘 Postgres",
      "🏠 ClickHouse",
    ]}
  />

  <div class="prose prose-invert mb-6 max-w-none">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-3">
          <Brain
            className="text-brand-500 h-5 w-5 translate-y-0.5 drop-shadow-[#06b6d4_1px_1px_12px]"
          />
          <h2 class="text-brand-500 text-xl font-medium">
            About my engineering philosophy
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
          I deeply believe in the philosophy of iterative development and
          incremental progress. I stand by the mantra that "Done is better than
          perfect". It's essential to deliver value quickly, but I also pay
          immense attention to code quality, architecture, and scalability to
          ensure the systems we build today don't become the bottlenecks of
          tomorrow.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-3">
          <Code
            className="text-brand-500 h-5 w-5 translate-y-0.5 drop-shadow-[#06b6d4_1px_1px_12px]"
          />
          <h2 class="text-brand-500 text-xl font-medium">
            Technical expertise
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
          My technical journey has led me to become proficient in a variety of
          technologies, with particular love for Elixir, TypeScript, React, and
          Postgres. Whether it's crafting elegant UIs with React, writing
          fault-tolerant, scalable backend logic with Elixir, or ensuring data
          consistency and security with Postgres, I'm comfortable throughout the
          stack. I've also worked on complex distributed systems, ensuring high
          availability and fault tolerance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-3">
          <GraduationCap
            className="text-brand-500 h-5 w-5 translate-y-0.5 drop-shadow-[#06b6d4_1px_1px_12px]"
          />
          <h2 class="text-brand-500 text-xl font-medium">
            Continuous Learning
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
          I am a firm believer in lifelong learning. In the ever-evolving world
          of technology, staying stagnant isn't an option. I am always ready to
          explore new technologies, methodologies, and best practices to sharpen
          my skills and stay on top of the game.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-3">
          <Users
            className="text-brand-500 h-5 w-5 translate-y-0.5 drop-shadow-[#06b6d4_1px_1px_12px]"
          />
          <h2 class="text-brand-500 text-xl font-medium">
            Leadership and Collaboration
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
          As a Staff Engineer, I strive to drive technical vision, mentor
          budding engineers, and facilitate a culture of collaboration and open
          dialogue. Rather than simply focusing on my personal output, I see my
          role as a force multiplier – accelerating the productivity and growth
          of the entire team by sharing knowledge and enabling others to work
          more effectively. I enjoy working with diverse teams and believe that
          the best solutions emerge from the amalgamation of unique
          perspectives.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-baseline gap-x-3">
          <Target
            className="text-brand-500 h-5 w-5 translate-y-0.5 drop-shadow-[#06b6d4_1px_1px_12px]"
          />
          <h2 class="text-brand-500 text-xl font-medium">
            Building with Purpose
          </h2>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
          Software engineering, to me, is more than just writing code—it's about
          solving problems and creating value. I approach every task, big or
          small, with a product mindset. I ask not just "how" to build, but
          "why". This helps me stay aligned with user needs and business goals
          and ensure that the technology we build serves a meaningful purpose.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <Blockquote
        quote="Great architecture isn't built overnight—it evolves with your business. I focus on writing code that scales gracefully, adapts to changing requirements, and grows sustainably alongside your company's ambitions."
        author="Dorian Karter"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
